---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Critical MAS blog">
	<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
		<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About Critical MAS</h1>

		<div class="post-content">
			<p class="text-xl leading-relaxed mb-6">
				Critical MAS was a personal blog by MAS (Michael Allen Smith), covering topics including
				nutrition, fitness, and various other interests.
			</p>

			<h2>About the Archive</h2>
			<p>
				This site is an archived version of the blog, spanning from 2005 to 2025. The blog is no
				longer actively maintained, but all posts and comments have been preserved for posterity.
			</p>

			<h2>About MAS</h2>
			<p>
				You can learn more about Michael Allen Smith (MAS) at <a
					href="https://michaelallensmith.com">michaelallensmith.com</a
				>.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>
